  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is aimed to assess the prevalence of thiamin deficiency in obese Thai children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is a cross-sectional study. The objectives of the study are to determine the
      prevalence of thiamin deficiency in obese Thai children and to assess the associations of
      dietary factors and thiamin deficiency.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
